#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid "A customer call you for an incident on a device?"
msgstr "ມີລູກຄ້າໂທຫາເຈົ້າກ່ຽວກັບບັນຫາທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນກັບອຸປະກອນບໍ?"

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid "A customer calls you to handle a device you didn't install?"
msgstr "ມີລູກຄ້າໂທມາໃຫ້ຈັດການອຸປະກອນທີ່ເຈົ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ເປັນຄົນຕິດຕັ້ງໃຫ້ບໍ?"

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A maintenance indicator is here to help you know at first sight whether "
"this\n"
"                device is under ongoing maintenance contract or not."
msgstr ""
"ຕົວບົ່ງຊີ້ການບຳລຸງຮັກສາແມ່ນຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເຈົ້າຮູ້ໄດ້ທັນທີວ່າ\n"
"                ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຢູ່ພາຍໃຕ້ສັນຍາການບຳລຸງຮັກສາຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Access devices history and related field services from the <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Contacts App</font>\n"
"                </strong>."
msgstr ""
"ເຂົ້າເບິ່ງປະຫວັດອຸປະກອນ ແລະ ການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງໄດ້ຈາກ <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່</font>\n"
"                </strong>."

