#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Assign the Refrigerant category to refrigerant products you need to monitor "
"from\n"
"                    the Inventory or Sales Apps."
msgstr ""
"ກຳນົດໝວດໝູ່ ນ້ຳຢາແອ ໃຫ້ກັບຜະລິດຕະພັນນ້ຳຢາແອທີ່ເຈົ້າຕ້ອງການຕິດຕາມຈາກ\n"
"                    ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ ຫຼື ແອັບການຂາຍ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid "Attaching brochures to your quotations for your customers;"
msgstr "ຄັດຕິດໂບຊົວໄປກັບໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຂອງເຈົ້າ;"

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Auto trigger for replenishment rule runs once a day and automatically "
"creates a\n"
"                    purchase order with appropriate quantities that you only "
"have to confirm.<br/>This\n"
"                    helps you not even to have to wonder whether to order or "
"not those to keep your\n"
"                    business running."
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບເຕີມສິນຄ້າອັດຕະໂນມັດຈະເຮັດວຽກມື້ລະຄັ້ງ ແລະ ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ\n"
"                    ດ້ວຍຈຳນວນທີ່ເໝາະສົມ ເຊິ່ງເຈົ້າພຽງແຕ່ກົດຢືນຢັນເທົ່ານັ້ນ.<br/>ສິ່ງນີ້\n"
"                    ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເຈົ້າບໍ່ຕ້ອງກັງວົນວ່າຈະສັ່ງຊື້ເຄື່ອງຕອນໃດ "
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທຸລະກິດດຳເນີນໄປໄດ້ຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ."

