#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Field Service App</strong> is the place to plan and follow up "
"work\n"
"            to be done on customer sites."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່</strong> ແມ່ນບ່ອນສຳລັບວາງແຜນ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມວຽກ\n"
"            ທີ່ຈະໄປເຮັດຢູ່ສະຖານທີ່ຂອງລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Field Services gives you access to all tasks related to this device to\n"
"                        capture the last maintenance and repair tasks."
msgstr ""
"ບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່ ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເຈົ້າເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກວຽກທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບອຸປະກອນນີ້ ເພື່ອ\n"
"                        ເບິ່ງຂໍ້ມູນການບຳລຸງຮັກສາ ແລະ ການສ້ອມແປງຄັ້ງລ່າສຸດ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Maintenance's links the sale order for Subscriptions of this\n"
"                        device."
msgstr ""
"ການບຳລຸງຮັກສາ ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບໃບສັ່ງຂາຍສຳລັບການລົງທະບຽນນຳໃຊ້ (Subscription) ຂອງ\n"
"                        ອຸປະກອນນີ້."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid "The Sales links the sale order for this device."
msgstr "ການຂາຍ ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບໃບສັ່ງຂາຍຂອງອຸປະກອນນີ້."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid "The Transfers lists you the deliveries of the device."
msgstr "ການໂອນຍ້າຍ ຈະສະແດງລາຍການການຈັດສົ່ງອຸປະກອນ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The map of interventions is as well available from the My Tasks menu, by\n"
"                default today's ones."
msgstr ""
"ແຜນທີ່ຂອງການດຳເນີນວຽກສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ຈາກເມນູ ວຽກຂອງຂ້ອຍ, ໂດຍ\n"
"                ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນຈະສະແດງວຽກຂອງມື້ນີ້."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The refrigerant consumption break down is available through time, by product "
"and\n"
"                with \"added\" and \"removed\" distinction. This reporting "
"relies on field service\n"
"                worksheets filled up by technicians."
msgstr ""
"ລາຍລະອຽດການນຳໃຊ້ນ້ຳຢາແອ ສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ຕາມໄລຍະເວລາ, ຕາມຜະລິດຕະພັນ ແລະ\n"
"                ແຍກລະຫວ່າງ \"ເພີ່ມເຂົ້າ\" ແລະ \"ຖ່າຍອອກ\". ການລາຍງານນີ້ແມ່ນອີງຕາມ\n"
"                ໃບບັນທຶກວຽກທີ່ຊ່າງເຕັກນິກເປັນຄົນຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid "Then the worksheet can be filled in while performing the work."
msgstr "ຈາກນັ້ນ, ສາມາດຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນໃສ່ໃບບັນທຶກວຽກໃນຂະນະທີ່ກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກໄດ້."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr "ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນຟຣີໃນແພັກເກດປັດຈຸບັນຂອງເຈົ້າ; ເຊີນທົດລອງໃຊ້ໄດ້ເລີຍ! 🙃"

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"They will open their tasks of the day to work on it from the Field Service "
"App."
msgstr "ພວກເຂົາຈະເປີດເບິ່ງວຽກຂອງມື້ນີ້ເພື່ອເລີ່ມເຮັດວຽກຈາກແອັບບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid "To help you with that, here is how to proceed:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍເຈົ້າໃນເລື່ອງນັ້ນ, ນີ້ແມ່ນຂັ້ນຕອນການດຳເນີນການ:"

#. module: hvac_services
