#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Worse case if those details are missing, input placeholder data and create "
"an activity to update those in the future!"
msgstr ""
"ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ຂໍ້ມູນບໍ່ຄົບຖ້ວນ, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຊົ່ວຄາວໄປກ່ອນ ແລະ ສ້າງກິດຈະກຳເພື່ອມາອັບເດດຂໍ້ມູນໃນພາຍຫຼັງ!"

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "ເຈົ້າຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການສຶກສາເພີ່ມເຕີມບໍ?"

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are ready to sign your first customers? To do so, open the Sales App,\n"
"                create a new order and the customer."
msgstr ""
"ເຈົ້າພ້ອມທີ່ຈະເຊັນສັນຍາກັບລູກຄ້າຄົນທຳອິດແລ້ວບໍ? ໃຫ້ເປີດແອັບການຂາຍ,\n"
"                ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຂາຍໃໝ່ ແລະ ເພີ່ມລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງເຈົ້າໄດ້ຈາກໜ້າແຜງຄວບຄຸມຫຼັກ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can define how to attach such documents to your quotations from the list "
"view."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າສາມາດກຳນົດວິທີການຄັດຕິດເອກະສານເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນເຂົ້າໃນໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໄດ້ຈາກໜ້າມຸມມອງລາຍການ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now see that the task is done. In the case of a repair, the time "
"spent and\n"
"            consumed products can be billed to your customer."
msgstr ""
"ຕອນນີ້ເຈົ້າຈະເຫັນວ່າວຽກໄດ້ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ. ໃນກໍລະນີຂອງການສ້ອມແປງ, ເວລາທີ່ໃຊ້ ແລະ\n"
"            ຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ໃຊ້ໄປ ສາມາດນຳໄປອອກໃບບິນເກັບເງິນກັບລູກຄ້າໄດ້."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can open the Planning by User to appreciate the planned tasks for the "
"coming\n"
"                weeks."
msgstr ""
"ເຈົ້າສາມາດເປີດ ການວາງແຜນຕາມຜູ້ໃຊ້ ເພື່ອເບິ່ງວຽກທີ່ວາງແຜນໄວ້ສຳລັບ\n"
"                ອາທິດຕໍ່ໆໄປ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.sale_order_form_view
msgid ""
"You can’t create a serial here. To add a new device, go to the Contact and "
"create it there."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າບໍ່ສາມາດສ້າງເລກຊີຣີຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້ໄດ້. ເພື່ອເພີ່ມອຸປະກອນໃໝ່, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ ແອັບຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ ແລະ ສ້າງຢູ່ທີ່ນັ້ນ."

#. module: hvac_services
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hvac_services.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your\n"
"                    Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
